Hello and welcome to NexTicket
I decided to make NexTicket as a side project. I often work with similar ticketing / service systems and I noticed flaws. NexTicket is a way of resolving some of those flaws. 

What is NextTicket? 
NexTicket is meant to be a lightweight, user friendly, and responsive ticketing system. Meant to be used by Service Desk and IT teams to take and keep track of tickets. 
